ss Sie mir helfen werden, Herr Doktor. Bitte... sagen Sie mir, was ich tun soll. (atmet tief ein, mit Anstrengung) [ foto_ende_02 ]", refusal=None, role='assistant', annotations=None, audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=[], reasoning_content=None), stop_reason=None)], created=1745502503, model='deepseek-r1-distill-llama-70b', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint=None, usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=487, prompt_tokens=3402, total_tokens=3889, completion_tokens_details=None, prompt_tokens_details=None), prompt_logprobs=None)
